  "texts": [
    "The dorsal portions were transferred to 0.2 mL of 60% acetic acid in deionized water and allowed to stand for 5 min.",
    "The tissue was then pipetted onto a positively charged microscope slide, and excess acetic acid was blotted away.",
    "To flatten the tissue and promote chromosome spreading, the slide was covered with a coverslip, and a lead brick was placed on top of it for 5 min.",
    "The slide and coverslip were then placed on dry ice for 5 min.",
    "The coverslip was removed from the frozen slide, and the slide was stained with 0.1 mg/mL Hoechst Stain solution for 5 min."
  ],
